(8) For the purposes of this section,â€”
(i) â€œIndustrial Areaâ€ means such areas, which the Board, may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in accordance with the scheme framed and notified by the Central Government;
(ii) â€œIndustrial Estateâ€ means such estates, which the Board, may, by notification in the Official Gazette, specify in accordance with the scheme framed and notified by the Central Government;
